articles.title: Osiris-Rex: Asteroid Bennu 'is a journey back to our origins' - BBC
articles.description: A handful of dust from an asteroid streaming through space could tell Nasa how life on Earth began.
articles.content:
Nasa's Osiris-Rex capsule will come screaming into Earth's atmosphere on Sunday at more than 15 times the speed of a rifle bullet.
